 (787.20), <a href="/web/20180712200624/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0546837&amp;fLockTerm=Malignant+neoplasm+of+esophagus%2c+unspecified+site">Malignant neoplasm of esophagus, unspecified site</a>
 (150.9)                    </div>
